OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FWriting in the British Medical Journal
OL,8,F(BMJ), they found no studies have
OL,9,Fexamined safety incidents relating to
OL,10,FPAs, while others have concluded PAs
OL,11,Fseem "to struggle" when working in GP
OL,12,Fsurgeries.
OL,14,FResearchers warned that one of the
OL,15,Fmain studies on PAs working in GP
OL,16,Fsurgeries only included information
OL,17,Ffor seven PAs.
