OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FThe review continued: "No evidence was
OL,8,Ffound that physician associates add
OL,9,Fvalue in primary care or that
OL,10,Fanaesthetic associates add value in
OL,11,Fanaesthetics; some evidence suggested
OL,12,Fthat they do not.
OL,14,F"The UK literature on physician
OL,15,Fassociates and anaesthetic associates
OL,16,Fis sparse and of variable quality, and
OL,17,Fsome is outdated.
