OL,7,FLast week, a coroner said the PA who
OL,8,Ftreated Pamela Marking before she died
OL,9,Fat East Surrey Hospital last year "had
OL,10,Fa lack of understanding of the
OL,11,Fsignificance of abdominal pain and
OL,12,Fvomiting and had undertaken an
OL,13,Fincomplete abdominal examination".
OL,15,FMrs Marking was seen by the PA and
OL,16,Ftold she had a nose bleed before she
OL,17,Fwas sent home, with her son believing
OL,18,Fshe had been cared for by a doctor.
