OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FMost associates work in GP surgeries,
OL,8,Facute medicine and emergency medicine
OL,9,Fand there are NHS plans to recruit
OL,10,Fmore.
OL,12,FIn November, the Government launched a
OL,13,Freview of the role of PAs and AAs led
OL,14,Fby Professor Gillian Leng, president
OL,15,Fof the Royal Society of Medicine.
OL,17,FHer report is expected to be published
OL,18,Fin spring.
