OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FFor the latest work in the BMJ, 29
OL,8,Fresearch papers on PAs and AAs were
OL,9,Fexamined but were found to be scant on
OL,10,Fdata.
OL,12,FThe total number of physician
OL,13,Fassociates studied was "very small",
OL,14,Fespecially in GP surgeries,
OL,15,Fresearchers said, and no studies
OL,16,Freported direct assessment of AAs.
OL,26,@uD@XOUuD@cO]
