OL,3,CLittle evidence that employing
OL,4,Cphysician associates in NHS is safe `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FMany patients were also unaware they
OL,8,Fwere seeing a PA, raising concerns
OL,9,Fabout transparency and informed
OL,10,Fconsent.
OL,12,FTrisha Greenhalgh, lead author of the
OL,13,Fstudy and professor of primary care
OL,14,Fhealth sciences at the University of
OL,15,FOxford, has been asked to speak to
OL,16,FProf Leng for her review.
OL,18,FProf Greenhalgh said: "The expansion
OL,19,Fof physician and anaesthetic
OL,20,Fassociates should be informed by solid
OL,21,Fempirical research.
OL,26,@zD@WOU
