OL,3,CLittle evidence that employing
OL,4,Cphysician associates in NHS is safe `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,F"At present, we simply do not have the
OL,8,Fdata to support claims that these
OL,9,Froles improve efficiency or maintain
OL,10,Fpatient safety.
OL,12,F"The absence of reported safety
OL,13,Fincidents in research studies does not
OL,14,Fmean they do not occur ` it means we
OL,15,Fare not doing the right kind of
OL,16,Fresearch to detect and analyse them."
OL,18,FProfessor Martin McKee, co-author of
OL,19,Fthe study from the London School of
OL,20,FHygiene and Tropical Medicine, shared
OL,21,Fthese concerns.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@eO]
