OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FHe said: "The mismatch between
OL,8,Fpolicymakers' enthusiasm for expanding
OL,9,Fthese roles and the lack of rigorous
OL,10,Fresearch evidence should be a red flag.
OL,12,F"Workforce shortages are a real
OL,13,Fchallenge, but they cannot be
OL,14,Faddressed by replacing doctors with
OL,15,Fpeople whose training maps poorly to
OL,16,Fthe duties expected of them, and who
OL,17,Fmay be inadequately supported, without
OL,18,Fa clear, evidence-based strategy."
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUzD@bO]
