OL,4,Cphysician associates in NHS is safe `
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FIn December, the Royal College of
OL,8,FPhysicians (RCP) published guidance
OL,9,Fsaying PAs should "never function as a
OL,10,Fsenior decision maker" and they should
OL,11,Fnever be allowed to decide which
OL,12,Fpatients can be admitted to hospital
OL,13,For sent home.
OL,15,FResident doctors, formally known as
OL,16,Fjunior doctors, should not supervise
OL,17,FPAs, the RCP added, with this
OL,18,Fresponsibility lying with senior
OL,19,Fdoctors.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@VO]
