OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FMeanwhile, PAs should not be able to
OL,8,Fprescribe medications, the RCP added.
OL,10,FThe guidance said that PAs must
OL,11,Fsupport, not replace, doctors and have
OL,12,Fa "nationally defined ceiling of
OL,13,Fpractice".
OL,15,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,16,Fhas also raised concerns about the
OL,17,Frole of PAs.
